Description: ColdFront tiered-storage command-line tools
 ColdFront provides transparent tiered storage for PostgreSQL (hot PG + cold
 Iceberg over object storage). This package contains the ColdFront tools:
 archiver (cold-tier writer), partitioner, and compactor (Iceberg
 maintenance) — PostgreSQL-version-independent, statically linked binaries.
